                            lanjut bayar
                            <span class="cartButton__triangle"></span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bgStatic">
                <div class="cashier center-flex heightFull">
                    <div class="cashierTitle articleTitle">Bayar menggunakan QRIS</div>
                    <div class="cashierImg opac0">
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/store-cashier-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/store-cashier.png" alt="" class="" width="810" height="779"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <div class="cashierDropzone"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cartImg storeCompo opac0">
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/cart-trolley-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/cart-trolley.png" alt="" class="" width="298" height="324"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                    </div>
                    <button class="button cashierButton cashierCompo opac0 -js-trig-scan"
                        aria-label="Click to trigger scanning">
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/scanning-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)"
                                alt="shift to scanning" width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/scanning.png" alt="" class="" width="338" height="464"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <picture class="cashierTrigger">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/scan-trig-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)"
                                alt="shift to scanning" width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/scan-trig.png" alt="" class="" width="119" height="245"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <div class="cashierScan"></div>
                    </button>
                    <div class="cashierInfo">
                        <div class="cashierInfo__shadow"></div>
                        <div class="cashierInfo__wrap">
                            Geser HP dan <br>
                            Scan QR Code
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bgStatic">
                <div class="success center-flex heightFull opac0">
                    <div class="successImg">
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/success-scanning-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/success-scanning.png" alt="QRIS" class="" width="581"
                                height="805" loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <picture class="successShine successShine1">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/success-shine-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/success-shine.png" alt="" class="" width="188" height="168"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <picture class="successShine successShine2">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/success-shine-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/success-shine.png" alt="" class="" width="188" height="168"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                    </div>
                    <div class="successTitle">
                        Satu
                        <picture class="successLogo">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/logo-qris-mob.png" media="(max-width: 768px)" alt=""
                                width="563" height="633">
                            <img srcset="./asset/images/logo-qris.png" alt="QRIS" class="" width="269" height="107"
                                loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                        <span>Untuk Semua</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bgStatic">
                <div class="journey center-flex heightFull">
                    <div class="journeyTitle articleTitle">Mari ikuti perjalanan QRIS mendorong inklusi melalui
                        perluasan akses pembayaran digital kepada seluruh lapisan masyarakat.</div>
                    <button class="button journeyButton opac0 -js-trig-people">
                        <div class="journeyButton__shadow"></div>
                        <div class="journeyButton__wrap">
                            Lanjut
                            <span class="journeyButton__triangle"></span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bgStatic">
                <div class="people center-flex heightFull">
                    <div class="peopleWrap center-flex">
                        <div class="peopleTitle">
                            <div class="reachTitle articleTitle">QRIS saat ini hadir di seluruh provinsi dan
                                kabupaten atau kota Indonesia. Layanan ini sudah dinikmati mulai dari pedagang kecil di
                                pasar
                                tradisional, mal, universitas, sekolah, tempat ibadah, lembaga sosia dan keagamaan,
                                tempat
                                pariwisata, bayar parkir, hingga retribusi Pemerintah Daerah. </div>
                            <div class="valueTitle articleTitle">Proses transaksi dengan QR Code menjadi lebih
                                mudah, cepat, serta yang terjaga keamanannya. <strong>Nilai transaksi QRIS naik
                                    175,44%</strong> secara tahunan
                                dengan <strong>jumlah pengguna mencapai 48,12 juta</strong> dan <strong>jumlah merchant
                                    31,61 juta</strong> hingga kuartal I/2024.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="container">
